C51 COMPILER V9.53.0.0   MAIN                                                              04/27/2026 11:44:43 PAGE 11  

 613   1      
 614   1          /*
 615   1            Startup greeting: "HI"
 616   1            H = ....
 617   1            I = ..
 618   1      
 619   1            Sidetone only.
 620   1            KEY_OUT is not activated.
